<i>noun</i>: 절구통 [절구통], 절구 [절구] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>절구통 [절구통]</dt><br>
<dd>1. mortar</dd><br>
<dd>절구질을 할 때 곡식 등을 담는 우묵한 통.</dd><br>
<dd>A bowl-shaped vessel in which crops, etc., are pounded with a pestle.</dd><br>
<dd>2. pig</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 뚱뚱한 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) A fat person.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>절구 [절구]</dt><br>
<dd>mortar</dd><br>
<dd>곡식을 빻거나 찧는 기구.</dd><br>
<dd>A tool used for pounding or grinding grains.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>